com.mumfrey.liteloader.core.api

Class LoadableModFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.File
      • com.mumfrey.liteloader.interfaces.LoadableFile
        • com.mumfrey.liteloader.core.api.LoadableModFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Injectable, Loadable<java.io.File>, LoadableMod<java.io.File>, MixinContainer<java.io.File>, TweakContainer<java.io.File>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.io.File>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoadableModClassPath

    public class LoadableModFile
extends LoadableFile
implements LoadableMod<java.io.File>
    Wrapper for file which represents a mod file to load with associated version information and metadata. Retrieve this from litemod.json at enumeration time. We also override comparable to provide our own custom sorting logic based on version info.
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
